%2F20170209%2Fs00013%2F1486576791699&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=938f3eca\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170209%2Fs00013%2F1486576791699&h=8c4dc783\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170209/s00013/1486576791699</a> (明報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">2. 中紀委公布民政部貪腐案處理結果，其宣佈民政部前部長李立國降為副局級非領導職務；前副部長竇玉沛則提前退休，兩人皆被吊銷中共十八大代表資格。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170209/s00013/1486576795458\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170209%2Fs00013%2F1486576795458&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=a860b1c2\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fpns%2Fdailynews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170209%2Fs00013%2F1486576795458&h=4886c8ff\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.mingpao.com/pns/dailynews/web_tc/article/20170209/s00013/1486576795458</a> (明報)<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170209/00178_011.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170209%2F00178_011.html&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d44de476\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170209/00178_011.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">3. 台灣的外交部領務局證實數十個駐外館處領務電子郵箱被不明人士登入，約一萬人的個人資料或已遭竊取。</span><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170209/00178_015.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Forientaldaily.on.cc%2Fcnt%2Fchina_world%2F20170209%2F00178_015.html&d=bnM7AcXj2gKZcTtpassgEG6tz0R9Svbxs0EcWe5CwMI%3D&h=d2db42ae\" target=\"_blank\">http://orientaldaily.on.cc/cnt/china_world/20170209/00178_015.html</a> (東方日報)<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">4. 中國當局暫停韓國樂天集團在中